      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">8</infon>
        <offset>1081</offset>
        <text>By the end of this period, 71% of the detected metabolites were significantly elevated in infected populations, and stable isotope-based flux measurements showed that these cells had elevated metabolic activity.
</text>
